g?quality=45&amp;resize=1239%2C826 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_gp5000_transparent_3-a8d65d2.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1859%2C1239 3x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_gp5000_transparent_3-a8d65d2.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=407%2C271, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_gp5000_transparent_3-a8d65d2.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=815%2C543 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_gp5000_transparent_3-a8d65d2.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1223%2C815 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_gp5000_transparent_3-a8d65d2.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1631%2C1087 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_gp5000_transparent_3-a8d65d2.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=407%2C271, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_gp5000_transparent_3-a8d65d2.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=815%2C543 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_gp5000_transparent_3-a8d65d2.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1223%2C815 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_gp5000_transparent_3-a8d65d2.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1631%2C1087 4x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_gp5000_transparent_3-a8d65d2.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=555%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_gp5000_transparent_3-a8d65d2.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1110%2C740 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_gp5000_transparent_3-a8d65d2.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1667%2C1111 3x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_gp5000_transparent_3-a8d65d2.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=555%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_gp5000_transparent_3-a8d65d2.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1110%2C740 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_gp5000_transparent_3-a8d65d2.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1667%2C1111 3x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><img data-src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_gp5000_transparent_3-a8d65d2.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C413\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Continental GP5000 Transparent tyre\" title=\"Continental GP5000 Transparent tyre\" src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_gp5000_transparent_3-a8d65d2.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C413\"></picture></div><div><figcaption><span><i></i> While not ‘Transparent’, the sidewalls of the new GP5000 are certainly translucent when you hold them up to the light.</span></figcaption><p><span><i>Warren Rossiter / Immediate Media</i></span></p></div><p>Continental states the new Transparent version weighs the same as the standard GP5000.</p><p>Our sister magazine, <a href=\"https://www.cyclingplus.com/\">Cycling Plus</a>, has a test of the <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/buyers-guides/best-road-bike-tyres/\">best road bike tyres</a> in its March issue (on sale now) and the sample set of 5000 clinchers in 28mm width weighs in at 241g. On our scales, the Transparent weighs in at 247.7g – well within Continental’s tolerances.</p><p>It still uses Conti’s latest Black Chilli compound and, compared to the excellent 4000S II before it, that makes for a claimed 12 per cent reduction in rolling resistance, 20 per cent better puncture protection, and a 10g drop in weight. Continental also claims the 5000 improves comfort over the previous generation tyre too.</p><div><picture><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_weight-c736a43-e1611912286559.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=298%2C199, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_weight-c736a43-e1611912286559.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=598%2C399 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_weight-c736a43-e1611912286559.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=897%2C599 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_weight-c736a43-e1611912286559.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1197%2C799 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_weight-c736a43-e1611912286559.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=298%2C199, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_weight-c736a43-e1611912286559.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=598%2C399 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_weight-c736a43-e1611912286559.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=897%2C599 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_weight-c736a43-e1611912286559.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1197%2C799 4x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(max-width: 375px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_weight-c736a43-e1611912286559.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=353%2C236, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_weight-c736a43-e1611912286559.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=707%2C472 2x, https://images.