;quality=45&amp;resize=1108%2C740 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_weight-c736a43-e1611912286559.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1664%2C1111 3x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_weight-c736a43-e1611912286559.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=554%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_weight-c736a43-e1611912286559.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1108%2C740 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_weight-c736a43-e1611912286559.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1664%2C1111 3x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><img data-src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_weight-c736a43-e1611912286559.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=618%2C413\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Continental GP5000 Transparent tyre\" title=\"Continental GP5000 Transparent tyre\" src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/continental_weight-c736a43-e1611912286559.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=618%2C413\"></picture></div><div><figcaption><span><i></i> Our test 28mm tyres tip the scales at 247.7g each.</span></figcaption><p><span><i>Warren Rossiter / Immediate Media</i></span></p></div><p>In terms of price, the Transparent is exactly the same as the standard edition, so that’s a recommended retail price of £59.99 per tyre. It’s available as a 700c tyre in 25mm and 28mm widths.</p><p>We asked Continental if they had plans for a tubeless version (it’s tube-only at the moment) and, while the company is currently holding its cards close to its chest, our source wouldn’t deny it’s not in their plans for the (near) future.</p></section><section><h3>Authors</h3><section><a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/author/warrenrossier/\"><img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/05/wozridi